n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#Benefits_Vanier_Graduate_Governmental_Scholarship\" title=\"Benefits| Vanier Graduate Governmental Scholarship\">Benefits| Vanier Graduate Governmental Scholarship<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#_Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply\" title=\"\u00a0Who is Eligible to Apply\">\u00a0Who is Eligible to Apply<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#Required_Documents\" title=\"Required Documents\">Required Documents<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#DurationVanier_CGS\" title=\"Duration\/Vanier CGS\">Duration\/Vanier CGS<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#How_to_Apply_Vanier_Canada_Governmental_Scholarship\" title=\"How to Apply| Vanier Canada Governmental Scholarship\">How to Apply| Vanier Canada Governmental Scholarship<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\/#How_to_be_nominated_Vanier_Governmental_Scholarship\" title=\"How to be nominated| Vanier Governmental Scholarship\">How to be nominated| Vanier Governmental Scholarship<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Vanier Canada Graduate Governmental Scholarship \u2026. This is to notify all students that the Canada Graduate Governmental Scholarship has released employment programs for all interested students who wish to apply;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999384\">Benefits<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999385\">Who is Eligible to apply<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999386\">Required Documents<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999387\">Duration<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999388\">How to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc79999389\">How to be nominated<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"benefits-vanier-graduate-governmental-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benefits_Vanier_Graduate_Governmental_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79999384\"><\/a>Benefits| Vanier Graduate Governmental Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The scholarships are worth $50,000\/year and enough to give the following:<\/li>\n<li>Dormitory<\/li>\n<li>A living allowance<\/li>\n<li>Trip allowance of 1 person for study in Canada<\/li>\n<li>University fees<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"who-is-eligible-to-apply\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply\"><\/span>\u00a0<a name=\"_Toc79999385\"><\/a>Who is Eligible to Apply<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Candidates who meet the following criteria are eligible:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>General eligibility criteria for Canadian government scholarships<\/li>\n<li>Canadian citizen\/foreign citizen<\/li>\n<li>Be nominated by only one Canadian institution that received Vanier CGS quotes<\/li>\n<li>Start the first doctoral studies or have completed not more than 30 months of their doctoral studies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"required-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_Documents\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79999386\"><\/a>Required Documents<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A Research Net application form (includes two reference letters each).<\/li>\n<li>Transcripts<\/li>\n<li>A research proposal (minimum 2 pages).<\/li>\n<li>Special circumstances (max 0.5 pages, optional).<\/li>\n<li>A CCV (limited entries: please see completing the Common CV.<\/li>\n<li>Research contributions (1 page).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"duration-vanier-cgs\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"DurationVanier_CGS\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79999387\"><\/a>Duration\/Vanier CGS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The period of this financial support is 3 years. And you can go for MS leading to Ph.D.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-vanier-canada-governmental-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_Vanier_Canada_Governmental_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79999388\"><\/a>How to Apply| Vanier Canada Governmental Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>If you are concerned to study in Canada Fully Funded Canadian Government Scholarships 2024, you must contact the institution you want to practice your studies there to elect you.<\/p>\n<p>For more information click <a href=\"https:\/\/vanier.gc.ca\/en\/home-accueil.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> and learn more.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-be-nominated-vanier-governmental-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_be_nominated_Vanier_Governmental_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79999389\"><\/a>How to be nominated| Vanier Governmental Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Those who wish to be applying for a Vanier CGS should verify that the institution to which they are applying for doctoral studies has a Vanier CGS quota.<\/li>\n<li>They must then notify the institution that they desire to be considered .<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/tru-graduate-programs-thompson-rivers-university\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">TRU Graduate Programs |Thompson Rivers University <\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"re